                            <comment id="12896121" author="rding" created="Fri, 6 Aug 2010 19:55:11 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;It turns out that the problem also affects the conditional operator (BinCond). &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12896123" author="rding" created="Fri, 6 Aug 2010 20:02:02 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The cause is the interaction between Accumulator UDF and binary operators. In the failure cases, the state kept by Accumulator is not reset cross record boundaries. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
